<p>In live trading, LEAN gets your account details to populate the <a href="/docs/v2/writing-algorithms/portfolio/"><code>Portfolio</code></a> object with your account balance and holdings and the <a href="/docs/v2/writing-algorithms/trading-and-orders/order-management/transaction-manager"><code>Transactions</code></a> object with your account open positions. LEAN subscribes to receive data for the securities with holdings and open orders after <a href="/docs/v2/writing-algorithms/initialization">Initialization</a> using the lowest resolution of explicitly added securities.</p>